<description>
<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DFnuAyHSVfl/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/476094107_1359847602044443_4795656176458400834_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=1&_nc_ohc=ts2dQX4-hF0Q7kNvgG1pbAJ&_nc_gid=b80e454eda6c462bb4660f9b7b19fe72&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYAht1yLovTwTWK4Rr3R7IGbz03Xb8PAhRpAYdeosMyA7Q&oe=67A7382F&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>#ad+ signature pasta + signature wine @apothicwine = three of you could have a chance to win a spot at a private cooking class with meHere’s how to enter:1. Comment on this post2. Start your comment with #DinnerWithApothicContestEntry3. Answer the following questions using at least 150 words and a maximum of 2,200 characters (including spaces)Why do you want the opportunity to discover your signature dish with the help of Olivia Tiedemann? What type of gathering are you most known for hosting? What are your favorite ingredient(s) to incorporate into dishes when you host? Who would you bring with you to help you discover your signature dish and the perfect wine pairing for it?NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. PURCHASE WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING. Open to legal residents of the United States (excluding UT, VA) and the District of Columbia who are 21 or older. Void where prohibited. Starts at 8:00:00 AM ET on 2/3/25 and end at 11:59:59 PM ET on 2/28/25. To enter visit https://www.instagram.com/apothicwine/, find the Apothic Your Signature Taste Contest Post on the page, and follow the instructions to submit your entry. Your Entry must start with the hashtag #DinnerWithApothicContestEntry. Subject to Official Rules. Official Rules available at https://apfco.com/secure/K401S/. Sponsor: GALLO.]]>
</description>
